snippet.title: Rose & Camellia Collection - WayForward Announcement Trailer
snippet.description: Slap your way to the top of high society! Grace and glamor give way to open-handed dueling across five games of aristocratic absurdity - Rose & Camellia 1, 2, 3, & 4, and Rose & Camellia vs. La-Mulana - in which you'll slap, dodge, feint, and counter your way through a series of one-on-one slap fights using Joy-Con motion controls or touch-screen swipes! Give the upper crust a richly deserved smackdown in Rose & Camellia Collection, coming exclusively to Nintendo Switch (release date TBD)! https://wayforward.com/wayforward-announces-rose-camellia-collection/
